camps we offer two types of honors thesis boot camps department or program specific boot camp and open boot camps the department or program specific boot camp is hosted for students from a single department or program the open boot camp is offered to any honors thesis writer winter open boot camp sunday march 4th 12noon 6pm please sign up in advance register by emailing writingcenter stanford edu if you have a group of friends writing theses and would like to participate in a boot camp together please write to us with some possible evenings or weekends that will fit your schedule workshops you can also request a workshop or ask your faculty advisor to request one from us workshop topics include writing the honors proposal managing the honors thesis and learning to write in accordance with the conventions of a particular field to request a workshop write to us at writingcenter stanford edu make an appointment drop in tutoring schedule pwr stanford university 590 escondido mall stanford ca 94305 3069 650 723 2631 contact us terms of use copyright complaints site by wired moon
